7th April 2020 
WATCHMAN stand-alone optical simulations repository

Email issues and suggestions to:
gary.smith@ed.ac.uk

Developed from the Geant4 OpNovice example, these programs are being used
to simulate WATCHMAN optics including but not limited to the reflective 
material Tyvek. Tyvek will be used in the Outer Detector which is used as 
a cosmics veto.